headline: Coinbase Deepens Crypto ISAC Ties As Valuation And Earnings Questions Linger
summary: Coinbase Global expanded its integration with Crypto ISAC to deliver continuous, automated threat intelligence to the blockchain industry. The move focuses on real time sharing of high confidence data on cyber risks, including state sponsored and advanced threats. The integration is available exclusively to Crypto ISAC members, aiming to support faster, more coordinated security responses across the crypto ecosystem.
